      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING ADMIRAL (1) sizzled around this track over 320m in 18.10 for a 5.5 lengths victory. Expected to go close again if runs up to latest time. SUPREME LADY (6) is a promising type who notched her 8th career success when too good (17.98) at this track last time. Form at the trip excellent including five wins. Has good speed so she should be prominent despite the draw. Can measure up again. WINSOME WANDA (8) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish 6 lengths back in third (18.50) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 320m. Has a solid record from this box including three wins and a minor placing. Leading chance. SHY SHEENA (2) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.",
